---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About WIPP">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="about-container">
      
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>About WIPP</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">A community for artists who value process over perfection</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Main Content Cards -->
      <div class="content-grid">
        
        <!-- What is WIPP Card -->
        <div class="content-card featured-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üé®</div>
          <h2>What is WIPP?</h2>
          <p>WIPP is a place for artists who want to get better at making things.</p>
          <p>It's not social media. There's no algorithm deciding who sees your work. Instead, it's built around the idea that good feedback is rare and valuable.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Why WIPP Exists -->
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üí≠</div>
          <h2>The Problem</h2>
          <p>Most platforms reward polish over process. Artists end up posting into a void, hoping for likes but rarely getting thoughtful feedback.</p>
          <p>We think critique is skilled labor that requires trust and attention.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- How it Works -->
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
          <h2>How it Works</h2>
          <p>WIPP has two spaces: a portfolio area for finished work, and workshop spaces for getting feedback on unfinished pieces.</p>
          <p>Everything is opt-in. You choose who sees your work and when to ask for feedback.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- What WIPP is NOT -->
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üö´</div>
          <h2>What We're Not</h2>
          <p>Not a marketplace. Not a social network. Not optimized for reach or discovery.</p>
          <p>Good work finds its audience here slowly, through genuine connection rather than algorithms.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Who it's For -->
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üë•</div>
          <h2>Who It's For</h2>
          <p>Artists more interested in getting better than getting famous.</p>
          <p>People who understand that feedback is a gift and are willing to give thoughtful responses to others' work.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Closing Message -->
        <div class="content-card closing-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üå±</div>
          <h2>Work in Progress</h2>
          <p>We're still figuring this out as we go. WIPP itself is a work in progress.</p>
          <p>The goal isn't perfection, but creating a space where unfinished work feels normal again.</p>
          <div class="cta-section">
            <p>If that sounds like something you'd want to be part of, you're welcome here.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mt-3 font-normal">
              WIPP is built and cared for by an independent creator who wanted a quieter space for artists to share unfinished work.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* About page with visual cards instead of letter format */
  .about-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    /* Remove the negative top padding from BaseLayout */
    margin-top: -2rem;
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
    @apply text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-200;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    @apply text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400;
  }

  /* Content Grid */
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  /* Content Cards */
  .content-card {
    @apply bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800 border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .content-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    @apply shadow-lg;
  }

  /* Featured Card */
  .featured-card {
    grid-column: span 2;
    @apply bg-stone-50 dark:bg-stone-800 border-stone-300 dark:border-stone-600;
  }

  /* Closing Card */
  .closing-card {
    grid-column: span 2;
    @apply bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border-green-200 dark:border-green-800;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Card Icons */
  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .featured-card .card-icon,
  .closing-card .card-icon {
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Typography */
  .content-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
    @apply text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-200;
  }

  .content-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    @apply text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300;
  }

  .content-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    @apply border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    @apply text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .featured-card,
    .closing-card {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .content-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>